      "text": "動画サイトで全試合が配信されてるんだよね\n芽衣もちょこっと観たよ",
      "startTime": 23.8666660946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お、コメント欄で\n芽衣とすずが絶賛されているぞ",
      "startTime": 27.5000004452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "わっ……ほんとだ\nえへへ、照れちゃうな～",
      "startTime": 33.7666671118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "でも……うん、やっぱり嬉しいな\nこうやってみんなに認めてもらえるのって",
      "startTime": 43.1666671118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "曲を作るまではいろいろあって大変だったけど……\nみんなの前で歌った時は本当に楽しかったんだ",
      "startTime": 50.8333368303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
